info.name: TOP PLUS SHARED & GENERAL EXTRAS PLUS
info.des: TOP PLUS SHARED & GENERAL EXTRAS PLUS
info.pricing: Includes rebate of 20% & LHC loading of $25
info.OtherProductFeatures: HCF provides the best coverage for medical services of any health fund in every state. Top Plus Shared is a premium level of hospital cover with no exclusions. Get access to Health and Wellbeing services.

inclusions.excess: $450 per admission to a maximum of $450 per calendar year

PreferredProviderServices.FreeText: More for teeth program fully covers a range of diagnostic and preventative dental services at participating dentists. Available from our 7 dental centres in Sydney and over 3500 providers in regional NSW, ACT, QLD, VIC & SA.

benefitLimits.combinedLimit: Physiotherapy, Chiropractic, Acupuncture, Massage and other services
Physiotherapy, Chiropractic, Acupuncture, Massage and other services
Physiotherapy, Chiropractic, Acupuncture, Massage and other services
Physiotherapy, Chiropractic, Acupuncture, Massage and other services

extras.OtherProductFeatures: A medium level of extras with generous limits on important services like dental, optical, physiotherapy and chiropractic. Orthodontic accrues at $250 per calendar year, up to lifetime limit of $1,500 for Orthodontist ($1,000 for General Dentist).
extras.SpecialFeatures: General dental includes dental check-ups which have service limits not included in annual limit. Only oral surgery and endodontics are covered under major dental. Other therapies include speech therapy (sub-limit of $200) & exercise physiology (sub-limit of $200.). Acupuncture, Chinese herbal medicine consultation & remedial massage have a combined sub-limit of $100. Lower benefits apply for physiotherapy, chiropractic & osteopathy after the 11th visit.
